# terminate
Terminates the active listener

# request <search term>
Opens a new tab on the default system browser and quiries the Google search engine for the search term

# exact request <search term> include <include term>, ..., exclude <exclude term>, ...
Opens a new tab on the default system browser and executes an advanced search of the search term.
Takes optional parameters for including and excluding certain keywords from the results. 
Note that you have to repeat the word include or exclude for every term you want to apply the command to
ie. exact search music exclude movies include bach include motzart

# get weather
Prints the current weather as well as the weather forcast for the next days in the terminal

# get current weather
Prints the current weather in the terminal
